  → development/languages/Perl[Perl's] implementation of the *filter* function is → development/languages/Perl/functions/grep[`grep`].

  The → Linux/shell[shell] command → Linux/shell/commands/grep[`grep`] and Windows console commands → Windows/dirs/Windows/System32/find_exe[`find.exe`] and
  → Windows/dirs/Windows/System32/findstr_exe[`findstr.exe`] might be considered a sort of a *filter* function (in which each line of a text file is an element of a list).

